# ROS 2 Humble + Gazebo Fortress.
# Notes:
#   • SDF plugin filenames change: gz-sim-*-system → ignition-gazebo-*-system.
#     Run scripts/distro-switch.sh to apply this rewrite to the worlds + model.
#   • OpenVINS builds fine here — no .h→.hpp patch needed (Humble is the
#     sweet spot the upstream targets).
ROS_DISTRO=humble
GZ_PKG=ignition-fortress
GZ_CMD=ign gazebo
ROS_DOMAIN_ID=42
